 origins and rise of the Culture Wars.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 4aIdentitätskrise. 4aSozialisation. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aCulture War.  aIdentity Crisis.  aSocialisation.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021 Englishz978311075418608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021z9783110753967oZDB-23-DSW0 cEPUBz97831107089360 cprintz978311070557740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311070889940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110708899423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110708899.jpg  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  a978-3-11-075072-0  DG Ebook Package English 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075418-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DSWb2021